high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn right to face the round table.
Take the small knife to the right of the bread on the table.
Cut the bread on the right into slices.
Put the knife on the right bread.
Take a slice of bread from the table.
Turn right, go forward a step, turn right, go forward, turn right to the fridge.
Put the bread on the left of the same shelf as the tomato. Close then open the fridge door. Take the bread from the fridge.
Turn right, go forward to the table, turn right, go forward to the counter, turn left, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the trash bin.
Put the bread in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread in a trash bin.

high_descs: Go to the left of the round table
Grab the knife off of the table
Cut the loaf of bread into slices
Put the knife on the table
Grab a slice of bread off of the table
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cool the bread in the fridge and then take it out
Turn around and go to the trash can
Put the bread in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Putting cold sliced bread in the trash can

high_descs: Turn and go to the round table.
Pick up a butter knife on the round table.
Cut a loaf of bread on the round table.
Put the knife on the round table.
Pick up a slice of bread on the round table.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill a slice of bread in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the trash can.
Put the slice of bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in the trash can.
